OL,3,CTwo tidal energy generators could be
OL,4,Ctested in Alderney waters
OL,6,FAlderney's Policy and Finance
OL,7,FCommittee (PFC) has confirmed its
OL,8,Fsupport in principle, but has asked
OL,9,Fthe company for a detailed
OL,10,Fpresentation before coming to a
OL,11,Fdecision.
OL,13,FPFC Chairman Nigel Vooght says: "This
OL,14,Fis an opportunity for Alderney to use
OL,15,Fa small part of its tidal resources to
OL,16,Fshow that Alderney is open for
OL,17,Fbusiness as a tidal energy test site."
OL,19,FThe proposal is asking for two of the
OL,20,Fpower generating screws to be mounted
OL,21,Fon a floating platform in Alderney.
