OL,3,CTwo tidal energy generators could be
OL,4,Ctested in Alderney waters
OL,6,FThe 'Axial Skelter' is made from
OL,7,Frecycled plastic, only uses one moving
OL,8,Fpart, and can be repaired locally with
OL,9,F3D printed parts.
OL,11,FSpiralis Energy will not be seeking
OL,12,Ffinancial aid from the States, who
OL,13,Fwill instead consider a fee for the
OL,14,Fuse of Alderney's waters for a maximum
OL,15,Fof 12 months.
OL,17,FThe States of Alderney hopes the trial
OL,18,Fcould lead to "economic opportunities
OL,19,Fand an additional source of renewable
OL,20,Fenergy for Alderney".
